name: SeattleFoodTruckFinder(Unofficial)
0:
”Alexa ask Food Truck Finder where is the nearest food truck”
”Alexa ask Food Truck Finder where will the closest food truck be tomorrow”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food truck finder
des:
A skill to tell you about nearby food trucks in the Seattle area. Ask where nearby food trucks are located. 

This skill will use the address specified in your Alexa app to find nearby food trucks.
